message.raw:
Mofified ADwin to reprogram in its static values after a buffered run.
The Tübingen group finds this preferable to maintaining output continuity.
I'm inclined to agree - it's really not good to accidentally leave a dispenser on!

Also made static programming a little faster - it appears to be able to handle it.
